tafsir[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Mi wonndirii Malaa'ikaaji sappiniraa…ói sappeejii, fii dewal majji."
  37,2,"Mi woondirii Mlaa'ikaaji soggiray…ói duule …óin, haa ka Alla muuyiri jipporde majje."
  37,3,"Mi woondirii Malaa'ikaaji janngooji daalol Alla …óin."
  37,4,"Pellet, rewetee…óo mon On, onon yim…ìe …ìen, e hoore goonga, ko bajjo, Mo alaa kafidii…óo: On woni Alla."
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, jey…óo kadi pu…óal e mutal naange ngen, hitaande nden fow."
  37,6,"Men labinirii kammu hikkii ngu aduna ngun, cu…óaari koode …óen, nannditayndi e ka≈ã≈ãe jal…ìu…óe."
  37,7,"Men reeniri kammu hikkii ngu aduna ngun, koode …óen, fii da…óugol kala seytaane yatundu e …óoftaare Alla."
  37,8,"∆äin seytanooji ha…ótanaaka he…óitagol matu Malaa'ika ka kammu, tuma …ìe wowlata ko Joomi ma…ì…ìe wahayini e ma…ì…ìe, immorde e sari'aaji; tawde ontuma, hi…ói feroree ba≈ã-woo ba≈ã."
  37,9,"∆äum ko fii ra…óagol wata …ói he…óito Malaa'ika'en. E hoore …óum, hino woodani …ói kadi laakara, lepte muusu…óe, duumii…óe, …óe ta∆¥ondirtaa."
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun seytaiiru biftii ndu e majji, jilannde haala, woni konngol e haala Malaa'ika'en, ko tawata fii mun hewtaali yim…ìe leydi …ìen; ontuma, ndu jokkintiniree hoodere hu…ì…ìunde, ko sunna ndu. Hino ara ka tawata ndu hewtinii ngol konngol jilaangol, e musidal mayru, haa ngol hewtoya ndaaroo…ìe …ìen, ado ndu fi…óireede hoodere sunnaynde nden, …ìe …ìeydita …óon, penaale teemedere."
  37,11,"An Muhammad, lamndo …ìee heefer…ìe yeddu…ìe fii ummital: si tawii ko kam…ìe …ìuri sa…ótude tagugol, e tii…óugol …ìalli, e mawnugol cemmbe, diini …ìen …ìe Men tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, wonndude e Malaa'ika'en? Men tagirii …ìe kam…ìe, loopal narnungal. Ko honno …ìe yeddirta fii ummital, e hoore ko e loopal lo'ungal narnungal …ìe tagiraa?"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, an Muhammad, e kattal Alla ngal, e no O toppitora fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun, haawi…óaa kadi, ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen yeddata kon fii ummital. Hakkee non ko …ìe sa…ótini fennugol fii maggal, hi…ìe jalnora ko wowlataa fii maggal."
  37,13,"Si …ìee sirkoo…ìe waajoraama kala noone e waaju, …ìe waajitortaa mo, sakko …ìe nafitora; hakkee ko …ìe yoori …ìer…óe."
  37,14,"Si …ìe yi'ii maande e maandeeji Annabiijo on (yo o his), tinndinde e goonga makko kan, …ìe fantina jalkitugol e haaweede."
  37,15,"∆Åe wi'a: Ko Muhammadu addi koo wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu."
  37,16,"yoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e wu…óu…óe, haray men immintinoyte …ìaawo …óum? Waawaa wonnde."
  37,17,"Baabiraa…ìe amen, adinoo…ìe men kadi …ìen, immintinoyte …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe?"
  37,18,"Maakan …ìe jaabo…óaa …ìe an Muhammad: Pellet, on immintinoyte …ìaawo nde on wontude mbullaari e ∆¥i'e wo…óu…óe. Baabiraa…ìe mon adinoo…ìe …ìen kadi wano non. On fow on immintiniroyte jaasere e hoyneede."
  37,19,"Anndee …óum, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet ka alaandu (…ói…óa…ìuru ndun) tawaa jaka yoo, fow ma…ì…ìe hi…ìe ndaara kulaleeji √ëalnde Darngal, hi…ìe habbitii ko Alla huuwata …ìe."
  37,20,"Sirkoo…ìe fennunoo…ìe ummital …ìen wi'oya ontuma: Ee halkaare amen ! Ko ndee woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe …óen, nde Alla yo…ìitaya jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, golle …óe …ìe ardinnoo ka nguurndam ma…ì…ìe aduna."
  37,21,"∆Åe wi'anee ontuma: ko ndee tigiri, woni √ëalaande √±aawugol hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen, nde √ëalaande nde fennayno…óon fii mun aduna."
  37,22,"Malaa'ika'en wi'anee nden √ëalnde: Moo…ìee sirkoo…ìe too√±ir…ìe sirku ma…ì…ìe on, e gartoo…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ka sirkugol e ka fennugol, e …óin sanamuuji …ói …ìe rewaynoo …ìe acca Alla. ∆Åe holloya …ìe laawol Yiite ngol, …ìe soggiroya …ìe ton, tawde ko ton woni jaa∆¥orde ma…ì…ìe."
  37,23,"37:22"
  37,24,"Darnon …ìe fii √±aaweede, ado …ìe naadeede ka Yiite. ∆Åaawo …óum, soggiron …ìe ka Yiite."
  37,25,"∆Åe feliroyee wi'aneede: ko he…ìi on, on wallindirtaa hakkunde mon, wano wallindirayno…óon aduna? Fewndo aa∆¥oto…óon wonnde sanamuuji mon …óin walloyay on?"
  37,26,"Ko woni kam…ìe on hannde, ko …ìe doftiiii …ìe yamiroore Alla hoy…ìe. Alaa ka …ìe wallindira, tawde …ìe alaa …óum feere."
  37,27,"Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtita yoga, …ìe wona e felindirgol wennjondira, ka …óin …ói…ói nafataa nden √±alnde."
  37,28,"Jokkunoo…ìe …ìen wi'ana jokkanoo…ìe …ìen: ko onon …ìee koohoo…ìe, wonunoo ko ardiranaynoo men, ka ba≈ã≈ãe diina e goonga; wonon e cu…óinangol men keeferaaku e sirkangol Alla e faggitagol geddi, doginon men e goonga ka Nulaa…ìe Alla …ìen addunoo kan."
  37,29,"Jokkanoo…ìe …ìen kadi jaabitoo …ìeya: wanaa non woniri. Ko woni kon, ko e keeferaaku wonuno…óon, on mee…óaali wonnde gom…óim…ìe, wurin, ko on yeddunoo…ìe wonunoo."
  37,30,"Doole woo men alanaano on e hoore ko jokkuno…óon men kon, haa men yolla on e keeferaaku maa sirku maa faggitagol geddi. Si ko woni, on wonuno yim…ìe fantim…ìe e yeddugol e majjere."
  37,31,"Koongol Joomi men ngol ka kammbol Makko wiide: ""Mi hebbiniroyte Jahannama, e kala …ìen jokku …ìe ma"" (Cortewol Saad, aaya 85), ko haanungol jojjude; …óum holli, ko en mee…óoo…ìe ko Joomi men kammbiri kon, feere mun alaa."
  37,32,"Men nodduno on e majjere e keeferaaku, tawde non, ko men majjunoo laawol goonga ngol, wonunoo."
  37,33,"Jokku…ìe e jokkanoo…ìe nden √±alnde, fow ko hawtoytee…ìe ka lepte."
  37,34,"Ko wano nii Men huuwirta …ìee bom…ìe, ka mee…óinirgol …ìe lepte …óen."
  37,35,"∆Åee sirkoo…ìe si wi'ananooma aduna: Rewtee…óo alaa si wanaa Alla, fii gollitirgol ngol konngol, sela kala ko lunndii ngol, …ìe salora …óoftagol …óum, townitanagol goonga kan."
  37,36,"∆Åe hujjinora keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun, wiide: kere men accitiray rewetee…ói amen …óin, fii yimoowo haangaa…óo? Wiide …ìe …óum, ko Nulaa…óo Alla on …ìe faandii (yo o his)."
  37,37,"Ko …ìe tukkiri Nulaa…óo on kon hino √±iddi. Tawde pellet, Nulaa…óo jom kisiyee on, mee…óaali wonnde haangaa…óo, wanaa yimmowo. Ko woni goonga, ko wiide ko Alqur'aanaare o ardi, noddaynde e wootin…óongol Alla, jokka Nulaa…óo Makko on. Nulaa…óo on non, o goonginii …ìeya Nulaa…ìe, e ko …ìe addunoo kon, immorde ka Alla, immorde e tawhiidi, e tabintingol ummital. O lunndakki e …óum."
  37,38,"Onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, pellet, ko on mee…óay lepte muusu…óe …óen, √ëalnde Darngal, sabu keeferaaku mun ngun e fennugol Nulaa…ìe …ìe."
  37,39,"Onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, on yo…ìitoytaake, si wanaa yeru kon ko huuwayno…óon aduna, e yeddugol Alla, faggitoo geddi."
  37,40,"Jeyaa…ìe Alla gom…óim…ìe, …ìen …ìe Alla la…ì…ìiniri fii ko rewa Mo, …ìe la…ì…ìinani Mo dewal ngal, …ìen …óon da…óoyay e …óen lepte."
  37,41,"Hino woodani …ìen jeyaa…ìe la…ì…ìinaa…ìe, fanndaari ndi Alla arsikata …ìe, tinndiraandi laa…ìugol e labegol e duumagol mun."
  37,42,"Oon arsuka ko muuyantee…ói ceertu…ói …ìur…ói laa…ìude, ko …ìe nafoo, e hoore …óum, ko …ìe teddiniraa…ìe mbarjaari toowundi, e yi'ugol yeeso Alla teddungo ngon."
  37,43,"∆Åe he…ìay …óin fow, ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói, √±ii…ìu…ói, tabitu…ói, …ói ta∆¥ondirtaa, sakko lanna."
  37,44,"hara hi…ìe waalii tuugi fewntondiri e hoore dan…óe."
  37,45,"Hara kore sanngara hino wannginee e ma…ì…ìe, laa…ìinr…óam wano ndiyam iloojam."
  37,46,"Ranwudam mbaadi , lew√±unde na dakmitoo heen e kala yaroo…ìe nde."
  37,47,"On sanngara, nanndaa e sanngara aduna on, tawde …óam sottintaa haqqil, wanaa muusinay…óam kadi hoore. Ko hisinay…óam …ìanndu e haqqille kala yaru…óo …óam."
  37,48,"Hino woodani …ìe ka Aljanna ton: rew…ìe …ìe alaa e …óuu…óa giteyaagal worbe janbe, yoo…óa gitee…ìe."
  37,49,"∆Åen rew…ìe no wa'i wa boofo soomaa…óa maraa sabu ranwude, …óe junngo meemaali."
  37,50,"Yoga e yim…ìe Aljanna …ìe fewtita yoga, …ìe lamndondira fii ko fe∆¥∆¥i aduna."
  37,51,"Go…ó…óo e …ìen gom…óim…ìe wi'a: Min mi…óo marunoo wonndii…óo yeddaynoo…óo ummital ka aduna."
  37,52,"Wi'anaynoo…óo lam, e hoore yeddugol jalkita: kere an wonndii…óo, hi…óa jeyaa e goongim…ìe immintineede maay…ìe …ìen?"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbulmbulndi e ∆¥i'e ki…ó…óe, haray ko en immintinoytee…ìe yo…ìitee njo…ìdi golle men …óen aduna?"
  37,54,"Wondinoo…óo makko gom…óim…ìe on, wi'ana wonndii…ìe mun …ìen ka Aljanna: on ∆¥eewiday e am, anndugol battane wonndinoo…óo lam yeddunoo…óo ummital on?"
  37,55,"Kanko o ∆¥eewa, o haynoo wondinoo…óo makko on, ka tummbere Dulbunge."
  37,56,"o wi'a: mi woondirii Alla ! An oo wondinoo…óo lam, a e…ì…ìuno halkitirgol fii am, naatugol Yiite, sabu ko noodirayno…óaa lam e keeferaaku, yedda fii ummital."
  37,57,"Si wanaa mo∆¥∆¥ere Alla nden e am, woni sabu mi feewiri gom…óinal, mi tawdeteno e leptetee…ìe …ìen, wano maa."
  37,58,"Wonaa non enen yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen, en maayataa."
  37,59,"En maayataa, si wanaa maayde men aranere nden aduna. Wurin ko en duumotoo…ìe ka Aljanna, en wonaali kadi leptetee…ìe, wano yeddu…ìe …ìen huuwirtee."
  37,60,"Pellet, ko ndii njo…ìdi ndi Joomi men warjori en naatugol duumoo Aljanna, da…óa Yiite …óoo, woni maloore mawnunde nden, nde yeru mun alaa."
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu ndii njo…ìdi mawndi …óoo, woni ko wa…ó…óii nde golloo…ìe gollanta. Tawde ko ndii woni ngeyngu tonatoongu."
  37,62,"Hara ko on neema mo Alla marani jeyaa…ìe Makko la…ì…ìinan …ìe Mo dawal …ìen, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude jipporde e teddungal, kaa ko leggal ""Zaqquumi"" hu…óaangal ka Alqur'aana ngal? Tawngal ko √±aametee heefer…ìe …ìen, ngal fayintaa ngal duncataa e ittugol heege!"
  37,63,"Men wa…óii ngal leggal, jarrabuyee, wonannde too√±ir…ìe geddi e keeferaaku …ìen. Tawde …ìe wi'uno: Yiite √±aamay le…ó…óe, …óum holli, leggal fu…óataa ka Yiite."
  37,64,"Laggal zaqquumi ngal, ko yaltirayngal ka kaaniri: ko ka tummbere Dulbunge, ngal yaltirta."
  37,65,"Dim…óe ngal leggal, hino kaaniri nannditi wa ko'e seytanuuji. Si hunnde non kaanii, ko …óum woni nde kaanii kadi kabaaru; …óum holli, √±aametee maggal on, ko ko √±iddi."
  37,66,"Kam…ìe heefer…ìe …ìen, pellet, ko e dim…óe ngal leggal haa…óungal, woni ko …ìe dekkirta, …ìe hebbinira deedi ma…ì…ìe heegaa…ói."
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani e caggal nyaamgol leggal ngal, njaram, jillaa…óam, fatinaa…óam haa √±iddi."
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde ma…ì…ìe nden, ko ka lepte Dul…ìoowe: …ìe iwa e lepte, …ìe yaha e lepte."
  37,69,"∆Åee heefer…ìe, …ìe tawu baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, majjunoo…ìe laawol peewal ngol; …ìe jokkitii …óon, ko aldaa e hujja."
  37,70,"∆Åe woni e yaccagol jokka batteeji majjere baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen ko yaawi."
  37,71,"Gom…óii ko …ìuri …óuu…óde e aram…ìe …ìen, majjiino, ado ma…ì…ìe. Wanaa yim…ìe maa …ìen, an Nulaa…óo, adii majjude e mofte …óen."
  37,72,"Gom…óii le, Men nunulo e …óen mofte adinoo…ìe, Nulaa…ìe, ko jertina e lepte Alla …óen, kono …ìe yeddi."
  37,73,"Ndaaru an Nulaa…óo, ko honno ba…ótane …ìen jertinanoo…ìe salii, no wa'unoo! Ko Yitte …ìe sakkitori naatude, luttiroo…ìe ton, sabu salaare e fennugol …ìe Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen."
  37,74,"Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla, la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen; ko …ìen …óon da…óoyta lepte …óen …óe …ìeya heefer…ìe yeddunoo wa…ótiniroya."
  37,75,"Gom…óii Nuuhu nodduno Men (yo o his) fewndo yim…ìe makko …ìen fennunoo mo, e hoore ko o noddi …ìe e mun kon, iskin ko Men woni mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe noototoo…ìe. Tawde Men yaccinno toraare makko nden e ma…ì…ìe."
  37,76,"Men da…óndi mo, kanko e …ìeynguure makko nden, wondude e gom…óim…ìe mo …ìen, lorra yim…ìe makko, e yoolagol tuufaan ngol, nelangol ngol e yim…ìe makko yeddunoo…ìe …ìen."
  37,77,"Men da…óndi …ìeynguure makko makko nden e gom…óim…ìe mo …ìen tun. ∆Åeya kan, Men yooliri …ìeya keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun."
  37,78,"Men heddinani mo e mofte hikkotoo…óe …óen, mantoore mo∆¥∆¥ere, nde …ìe mantirta mo."
  37,79,"Nuuhu hisii o da…óii wowleede bone, e mofte sakkitii…óe …óen. Wurin, mantoore e jantoore mo∆¥∆¥ere, heddoto fii makko."
  37,80,"Ko sugu ndii njo…ìdi, ndi Men warjorii Annabi Nuuhu, woni ko Men warjorta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe dewe mun …óen, …ìe rewi Alla tun."
  37,81,"Kanko Nuuhu, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe, woni e …óoftaare Alla …ìen."
  37,82,"Refti Men yooliri hedditii…ìe …ìen, waame mbo Men wurti e ma…ì…ìe on. ∆Åe fow ma…ì…ìe …ìe gasi."
  37,83,"Awa Ibraahiima, ko jeyanoo…óo e jokku…ìe diina makko, rewi laawol makko ka wootin…óingol Alla."
  37,84,"Janto nde o ardunoo ka Joomi makko, …ìernde hisunde e sirku, laa…ìan…óo Alla e tagu Makko ngun."
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo baaba makko e yim…ìe mun sirkaynoo…ìe …ìen: Ko hon…óum rewton gaanin Alla?"
  37,86,"E ko rewetee…ói fefindaa…ói, faala…óon rewude ko wanaa Alla?"
  37,87,"Ko sikku…óon, onon yim…ìe am, e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon, si on hawroyii e Makko, hara on rewaano Mo? Ko sikku…óon O gollata on ontuma?"
  37,88,"Annabi Ibraahiima ndaariri ka koode, himo taskoo …óa…ì…ìa feere, no da…óira yaltidugol e ma…ì…ìe."
  37,89,"O ngantinori yaltidugol e yim…ìe makko …ìen ka iidi ma…ì…ìe, wiide: ko mi nawnu…óo."
  37,90,"∆Åe acci mo caggal …óon, …ìe hucciti."
  37,91,"O moltii e rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin gaanin Alla, o jalnori …ói maakugol: E on √±aamataa ko sirkanoo…ìe on …ìen mo∆¥∆¥inani on kon?"
  37,92,"Ko he…ìi on, on wowlataa, on jaabotaako? Ko sugu …óum …óoo rewetee gaanin Alla?"
  37,93,"Ibraahiima moltorani …ói, piyirgol …ói junngo makko √±aamo ngon, fii muncugol …ói."
  37,94,"Rewaynoo…ìe …óin sanamuuji …ìen, fewri ka makko, hi…ìe yaawno."
  37,95,"Ibraahiima fewtitiri …ìe tabitaal, o feli …ìe, o maaki: E on reway kon ko lesir…óon juu…óe mon, accon Alla?"
  37,96,"Ko Alla tagi on, O tagi golle mon …óen, wano …óin sanamuuji …ói leston. Ko Kanko tun hanndi e Mo rewon, hara on renndidaani Mo e go…ó…óum goo."
  37,97,"Nde …ìe ronkunoo tee…óoragol mo hujja, …ìe yahri doole, …ìe diisonsiri haa …ìe fottani ko …ìe wa…óata ibraahiima; …ìe wi'i: mahanee mo maadi, hebbiniron ndi carma, hu…ì…ìon …óe yiite, refti bu…óon mo ton."
  37,98,"Yim…ìe Annabi Ibraahiima …ìen faandanii mo bone, no …ìe gaynira fii makko,…ìe …ìoortondira e makko, kono Men wa…ói …ìe kam…ìe sooyu…ìe …ìen; nde Men wa…óannoo mo yiite ngen …ìuu…ìol e kisiyee."
  37,99,"Ibraahiima maaki: Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, mi yalta e leydi yim…ìe am …ìen, no mi he…ìira feere rewugol Mo; aray nde O fewnata lam e ko mo∆¥∆¥anta lam aduna e laakara."
  37,100,"Joomi am, arsikam …ìi…ó…óo mo∆¥∆¥o, ko wallitoo lam, semmbina lam e yim…ìe am …ìen, tuma mi ferata."
  37,101,"Men jaabiniri toraare makko nden, humpitugol mo ko welata mo, fewndo Men wewlinirnii mo ge…óaljo mawnoowo, mu√±√±oytoo…óo; on woni Ismaa'iila (yo o his)."
  37,102,"Nde Ismaa'iila mawnunoo, o yottodi e ben makko jahal, ben makko Ibraahiima hoy…ói, koy…óol Annabaa…ìe …ìen non, ko wahayu. O humpiti ge…óal makko wiide mo: ko an yo …ìi…ó…óo am, mi yi'ii e koy…óol, wonnde mi…óo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'u…óaa e …óum. Ismaa'iila jaabii baaba'en mun, wiide: Baaba'en, wa…óee ko yamira…óon kon fii hirsugol lam, on taway lam, si Alla ja…ìii, jeyaa…óo e mu√±oo…ìe e weltor…ìe √±aawoore Alla nden."
  37,103,"Nde …ìe jebbilaninoo yamiroore Alla nden, Ibraahiima hippiri ge…óal makko, tiinde nden, fii hirsugol mo."
  37,104,"Men noddi Ibraahiima fewndo o hittiniraynoo wa…óugol yamiroore Alla nden, ka hirsugol ge…óaljo makko on, wiide: ko an yo Ibraahiima!"
  37,105,"Pellet, a laatinirii koy…óol maa ngol, fi…ìugol hirsude ge…óaljo maa on. Awa ko wano Men yo…ìitirt maa non firtingol ma nden huunde sa…ótunde, woni ko Men yo…ìitirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen; Men …ìoora …ìe e kulaleeji e sa…óteendeeji."
  37,106,"Pellet, ko …óum …óoo woni jarrabuyee …ìanngu…óo on. Ibraahiima hawrii e mun."
  37,107,"Men soktiri Ismaa'iila, dammol mawnungol, ko hirsee, hara wanaa kanko."
  37,108,"Men accani Ibraahiima, mantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitii…óe …óen."
  37,109,"Alla hiwrike mo, O du'anike mo kadi kisal e kala lorra."
  37,110,"Ko wano Men yo…ìitiri Ibraahiima e …óoftaare makko nden, Men yo…ìitirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen."
  37,111,"Kanko Ibraahiima, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe, hunnu…ìe sifaaji jeyeede Alla."
  37,112,"Men wewlintiniri mo ge…óaljo goo, wonoowo Annabaajo, e jeyaa…óo mo∆¥∆¥o; on woni Ishaaqa. ∆äum ko njo…ìdi …óoftagol mo Alla ngol, ka hirsugol Ismaa'iila, …ìi…ó…óo makko bajjo on nun."
  37,113,"Men jippini barki e makko, e dow ge…óal makko Ishaaqa. Men …óu…ó…óinani …ìe neema; wano …óuu…óireede …ìi…ó…ìe. Hino e geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol non, mo∆¥∆¥in…óo …óoftagpl Joomi mun, e too√±ir…óo hoore-mun yeddugol faggitoo …ìanngina bone."
