  37,149,"Muhammad, lamndorii …ìee sirkoo…ìe ""≈ãi√±ugol"": E on wa…óanay Alla …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìe a√±an…óon hoore-mon, heertinanon …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen fii mon? Ko hon…óum e senndoore nii?"
  37,150,"Ko honno …ìe aa∆¥orta wonnde Malaa'ika'en ko rew…ìe, …ìe tawanooka tageede majji, …ìe seeditaaki …óum?"
  37,151,"Pellet sirku…ìe …ìe e pennugol mum en e fepindaade …ìe penaale e dow Alla …ìe ngaskina …ìi…ó…óo e dow Makko, …ìe ko fenoo…ìe e ko…ìe noddittoo ko."
  37,152,"37:151"
  37,153,"Hara Allah su…ìan hoore Makko, …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìen …ìe a√±an…óon hoore-mon, e dow …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìe yi…óan…óon hoore-mon …ìen? Kallaa! wanaa non!"
  37,154,"Ko he…ìi on, onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, hi…óon √±aawira ndee √±aaaworaa oo√±iinde, wa…óanon Alla …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, su…ìao…óon hoore-mon wor…ìe …ìen?"
  37,155,"E on miijitotaako wonnde ko e meere won…óon e mun? Tawde si on taskike, on yi'iray non bonnde fi…ìnde mon nden."
